headline.print_headline: Ivory Coast Surrenders Youth Leader to ICC
headline.main: Ivory Coast Surrenders Youth Leader to ICC

lead_paragraph: The International Criminal Court says Ivory Coast authorities have surrendered to the court a former youth leader wanted on crimes against humanity charges linked to postelection violence.
